{"tid":849947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 恐怖工業意外　2地盤工遭鋼筋插穿膊","createTime":"2018-10-06T05:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T06:45:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"540ce4a55dcb28e369940fef3f39a91eb0d24eb3","tid":849947,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"何文田發生恐怖工業意外，今日(6日)早上8時50分，常樂街一居屋建築地盤，一名姓黃(21歲)油漆工人在吊船工作期間，疑跣腳失足從高處墮下大廈平台，遭一條約2公分直徑的鋼筋由左邊膊頭插入體內，登時動彈不得，工友見狀代為報警。消防及救護員接報到場，用工具將鋼筋鋸斷後，將工人送院治理，工人送院時仍然清醒，左膊插着一截鋼筋，醫生正設法將鋼筋拔出，警方列作工業意外，與勞工處展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n另外，馬鞍山落禾沙里一地盤亦發生同類意外，今日(6日)早上8時58分，一名姓陳(59歲)釘板工人，在上址工作時意外絆腳跌倒，身體向前仆，左邊膊頭被一支約1米長鋼筋貫穿，工友大驚合力將傷者扶起，鋼筋隨即被拔出體外，然後報警，陳由救護車送往沙田威爾斯親王醫院搶救後，需留院治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181006/bkn-20181006092106661-1006_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181006%2Fbkn-20181006092106661-1006_00822_001.html&d=gp6lRm7seQHhmILTjdPMLP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=0c245d7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181006/bkn-20181006092106661-1006_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"aa8509aedbbb0ea687f61c6b446c92f8772860f2","tid":849947,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ae76a6b8dd0893641866a7c23fc0e08ba4e1d5","tid":849947,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/06/134934_1eac3342e2d0e7a86ab6afb80e3e3e93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F06%2F134934_1eac3342e2d0e7a86ab6afb80e3e3e93.png&h=1401cc55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab8c8903f9bc24bf69b999aeaec558528aefb6